Based on practical examples, the subject provides an overview of how a clinical pharmacist can apply knowledge of pharmacoeconomics in his daily work. Students solve a sample task as homework. In the webinar, there will be a discussion based on a sample task.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The purpose of the subject is to provide an overview of what a clinical pharmacist must know about pharmacoeconomics and how to use this knowledge in everyday work.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  A student who has passed the subject: 1) knows the general principles of pharmacoeconomics 2) can apply the basic principles of pharmacoeconomics in everyday work
